---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Disclaimer">
  <article class="article-body prose-section">
    <header class="article-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="article-title">Disclaimer</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="article-content">
      <p>
        The TDD treats this page as part of the site's utility navigation alongside About and Methodology. It also
        identifies several disclosure and privacy responsibilities that belong here when they apply in production.
      </p>

      <p>
        Hardcopy book purchases are handled externally through Amazon. The design document states that if Amazon
        Associates is used later, the required affiliate disclosure should be added on this page. At present, books and
        artifacts are free resources on the site, with larger downloadable files intended to be served from Cloudflare
        R2.
      </p>

      <p>
        On privacy and analytics, the TDD specifies cookieless Cloudflare Web Analytics and a newsletter provider that
        handles consent within its own workflow. The document also says that data handling for newsletter signup should
        be documented on the Disclaimer or Privacy page. Comments are intentionally off at launch because some content
        may be sensitive and unmoderated discussion would create avoidable liability.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .article-header {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .article-title {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    margin: 12px 0 16px;
  }

  .article-content {
    max-width: var(--measure);
  }
</style>
